longBusinessSummary: Cabo Verde Capital Inc. operates as a content streaming company. The company operates through three divisions: Distribution, Live Stream, and Studios & Productions. It has a streaming platform that has various channels, including sports, music, lifestyle, family, and comedy, as well as international based channels. The company is based in Las Vegas, Nevada.
